### Health check (no API key required)
GET {{baseServer}}/api/healthz

### Health check (no API key required) - Local development
GET https://localhost:5000/api/healthz

### T1 - List tools (with API key)
POST {{baseServer}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
   "jsonrpc": "2.0",
   "id": 1,
   "method": "tools/list",
   "params": {}
}

### T1 - List tools (local development with API key)
POST https://localhost:5000
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
   "jsonrpc": "2.0",
   "id": 1,
   "method": "tools/list",
   "params": {}
}

### T2 - Download YouTube audio and convert to MP3 (local)
POST https://localhost:5000
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
   "jsonrpc": "2.0",
   "id": 2,
   "method": "tools/call",
   "params": {
      "name": "mcp_server_hub.Tools.YouTubeTools.DownloadToMp3",
      "arguments": {
         "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ",
         "outputPath": "output_audio_16khz_mono.mp3"
      }
   }
}

